    {
      "id": "62a8d073-58f5-4fdd-b74d-a97644a01499",
      "title": "Double tap/click to create new Chit",
      "note": "Any Chit with a note will show up here.And that's one of the underlying things that makes this tool great. The only things that show up in a view are the things that have content for that view. So notes show up under notes, things of dates show up on the calendar, things of statuses show up in Tasks, etc.",
