    {
      "id": "62fd3530-1976-4746-8626-56b0ca6298d5",
      "title": "What's the Point?",
      "note": "Omni Chits are a calendar, sticky notes, checklists, alarms, tasks, projects, etc. All as a single unified \"Chit\" entity type. Every item is all of those things. (Also has full vCard support for contacts)Its a calendar, sticky notes, checklists, alarms, timers, tasks, projects, etc. All as a single unified \"Chit\" entity type. Every item is all of those things. (Also has full vCard support for contacts).Basically, anything you'd want to track in terms of things to do or track or pay attention to, it does it all.Chits are The Thing. They aren't just event, but that, and notes, and checklists, and all those other  things all rolled into a single unified entity called a Chit.The Views let you see each of the Chits that have the applicable part in it. So on the calendar view you see any chit that has a time or a due date. On the checklist view you see any chit that has a checklist. Etc. Any chit van have any of the data types in it.",
      "tags": [
        "Notes"
      ],
